item.description: Hi Members, Holliston Meadows asked if we could met on April 29th rather than April 15th because School Vacation Week is April 13th- April 22 and they are full at that time - they use the training room where we meet at that time. Please bring a chair for the April 29th 2-4 pm meet. I will charge $5.00 per household to pay for the monthly Meetup.com dues. Those ythat are unemployed or economically challenged at this time need not pay. Tiny dog best, Kim
